  "text": "(P4) A fixed variable: \u2203j : l j = w j . x j can be substituted out of the problem. Then we have a reduced LP problem as follows, minc \u22a4x s.t.\u00c3x =b, l \u2264x \u2264w, wherex,l,w \u2208 R\u00f1 and\u00c3 \u2208 Rm +\u00f1 has full row rank. The last step is to reformulate the above problem as in the form of problem [CITATION_1] . After the presolving, it is guaranteed thatl > \u2212\u221e. Now we can define U = {j :w j < +\u221e} andx =x \u2212l, and obtain the desired LP problem,",
